CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 27 reads: "Dazzling Displays Exhibit Top Products at Fair...10. The Sanitizer Airway Industries, makers of Airway Vacuum Cleaners, were represented by Charles Orowetz, N.W. Carroll and Walter Petty sitting in their booth...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Charles Orowetz, N.W. Carroll, and Walter Petty seated in Sanitizer Airway Industries booth, in the Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
